"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Data from: Klein JO, Bacterial pneumonias, In: Textbook of Pediatric Infectious Diseases, Feigin RD, Cherry JD, Demmler GJ, Kaplan SL (Eds), WB Saunders, Philadelphia 2004, McIntosh K, N Engl J Med 2002; 346:429, Gaston B, Pediatr Rev 2002; 23:132, Boyer KM. Nonbacterial pneumonia. In: Textbook of Pediatric Infectious Disease, Feigin BD, Cherry JD, Demmler GJ, Kaplan SL (Eds), WB Saunders, Philadelphia 2004, and Sandora T, Harper MB. Pediatr Clin North Am 2005; 52:1059.",
